Question: One train is heading right and one train is heading left.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/48/3a/b2/483ab25d6c1ee17c01ba5f9c6040f83e.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/a9/07/4a/a9074aa8c8718f6617040f565bb5dcc3--pennsylvania-railroad-electric-locomotive.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the train heading right?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the train heading right?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the train heading left?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the train heading left?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
